upgrade.description:
Confirm the new versions are deployed:
```bash
helm list -n ${NAMESPACE}
kubectl get pods -n ${NAMESPACE}
```

Check that all pods have restarted with the new images and are in Running state.

troubleshooting.description:
Verify the HTTPRoute is applied and the gateway is ready:
```bash
kubectl get httproute -n ${NAMESPACE}
kubectl get gateway -n ${NAMESPACE}
```

Ensure the gateway service has an external IP or is port-forwarded.
